<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-pl-bases">1.★ <strong>[C] (pl bases) 根据；基础：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>on a regular basis</strong> 
定期地；经常地</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Naismith later wrote 13 rules which are the basis of modern basketball rules. 
奈史密斯后来定了13条规则，这些规定成为现代篮球规则的基础。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>On the basis of</strong> those facts, we can reach the following conclusion. 
根据那些事实，我们可以得出以下结论。</p></div></div>